<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n40068a"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n40" href="#n40068a">N40 (VI.B.28B)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n40all.htm#n40068a"> 68(a)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> I will place my / throne above the / clouds </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: Tertullian attributes to Satan the words given to the King of Babylon in Isaiah 14.13-14: &ldquo;I will set my throne above the stars &hellip; I will go up above the clouds, I will be like the Most High&rdquo; (Tert., Marcion 5.17). </mm> </dd></dl>
